    "description": "Newly renovated 3 bed home | 5 mins Gateshead Metro Interchange | Town Centre |<br /><br />High end | Modern open living and dining space | 55 inch Smart TV | 3 bedrooms | Super-king | Double |  Single bedroom | <br /><br />Doorstep location | City breaks | Shopping | Concerts <br />| Work | Visiting family | Quiet location<br /><br />Free weekend parking adjacent to property | Free mid week parking 2 mins walk |<br /><br />Excellent distance and central links to explore Newcastle Historic City Centre | Gateshead Quays | Museums | Coast |<br /><br /><b>The space</b><br />The property is a newly refurbished end of terrace in a private residential area, comprising of 3 bedrooms, 1 main bath <br />room with separate shower and separate downstairs toilet. It has a front garden and private rear, back yard / garden, with outdoor furniture . There are security cameras front and back to the property.<br />Parking is available at the side and rear of the property. Parking is free from Friday 6pm until Monday 9am. Mid week parking charges apply between 9am - 6pm. Parking can be paid on a parking app, or a free car park is available 150 yards away. <br />There is a local tescos 150 yards away, with many local takeaway and restaurant\u2019s. <br />An 8 minute walk takes you to the VUE cinema, Tesco superstore and restaurants, the walk provides  impressive views of the Tyne bridge.<br />5-6 minutes walk to Gateshead Interchange, to access the Metro underground , and regional bus networks. (It takes 5-6 minutes to travel into the centre of Newcastle from Gateshead Interchange)<br />Local micro pubs available locally. <br />Gateshead International Stadium and the Glasshouse concert halls are all within walkable distance approx 15 mins<br /><br /><b>Guest access</b><br />Guests can use the newly renovated private back garden / yard in the property. There is outside egg chair.<br /><br /><b>Other things to note</b><br />No parties, gatherings or loud music is permitted inside or outside the property. We ask guests to respect the privacy of neighbours and the wider neighbourhood. Please smoke or vape in the private rear garden of the property (and not in the front garden).",
